<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>컨트롤러에서 보낸 리스트 출력 인라인 방식</h1>
	<h2>[[${list}]]</h2>
	<h1>th:each사용</h1>
	<ul>
		<li th:each="str: ${list}" th:text="${str}"></li>
	</ul>
</body>
<h1>th:block사용</h1>
<ul>
	<th:block th:each="str: ${list}">
		<li>[[${str}]]</li>
	</th:block>
</ul>
<h1>th:each with status</h1>
<ul>
	<li th:each="str, status: ${list}">[[${status.count}]] --
		[[${str}]]</li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li th:each="str, status: ${list}"><span th:if="${status.odd}"
		th:text="${str}"></span> <span th:unless="${status.odd}"
		th:text="${str}"></span></li>
</ul>

<ul>
	<li th:each="str, status: ${list}"><span
		th:text="${status.odd} ? 'ODD ---' +${str} : 'EVEN ---' +${str}"></span>
	</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<ul>
	<li th:each="str, status=:${list}"><th:block
			th:switch="${status.index %3}">
			<span></span>
		</th:block></li>
</ul>

</html>